reviewText: Grandchildren love this Veggie Tales video.

I enjoy the Veggie Tales DVDs! I play them in our church nursery when the kids are tired and need to sit down and chill for a bit. Their subtle humor makes them tolerable even the twentieth time I see them, which I find invaluable. Thanks for some non-saccharine religious children's entertainment!
3 great veggie tales on one dvd!  Great price and good way to save space!  Recommended for veggie tales lovers!

The Vegie Tales are great family entertainment and they have wonderful messages in each story.  They are fun to watch, and there is a lot of humor hidden in the script.  Wholesome humor for the adults.  I love all of the Vegie Tales.  The kids are getting good lessons on how to act in todays wild world.
